# Alembic Database Migrations

This directory contains database migrations for PredictaX Backend.

## Commands

### Create a new migration (auto-generate)
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback one migration
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View current migration status
```bash
alembic current
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history --verbose
```

## Notes

- Alembic automatically detects changes in SQLAlchemy models
- Always review auto-generated migrations before applying
- Migrations are stored in `alembic/versions/`
- The database URL is loaded from the DATABASE_URL environment variable
